route: User


Get--/user/profile                  -view profile
Get--/user/followers                 -view followers
Get--/user/following                 -view following
Get--/user/wallet                    -view wallet
Get--/user/badge                     -get badge
Get--/user/badges                    -view badges
Get--/user/badges                    -view badges
Get--/user/reward/redeem             -redeem reward
Patch--/user/update                  -update user data
Post--/user/p/badge/{badge}          -Buy badge
Post--/user/{user}/follow            -follow user
Post--/user/{user}/unfollow            -unfollow user
Post--/user/{user}/chat                -chat users



route:Community


Post--/community/{id}/join             -join community
Post--/community/{id}/leave            -leave community
Get --/community/{id}/leaderboard      -leaderboard community
Get --/community/{id}/chat             -chat community
Get --/community/{id}/feed             -feed community


 


route:club

Get--/clubs                                -view clubs
Get--/club/{club}                          -view unique club
Get--/club/fans                            -view club fans
Get--/club/fan/leaderbord                  
-view club fan leaderbord list
Get--/club/feed                            -view club feed
Post--/club/{club}/post                    -post in club



